Roll a dice. On a 3+, remove that unit from the battlefield and set it up again on the battlefield more than 9" from all enemy units.
Pick up to 3 friendly **^^Skink Infantry or Skink Cavalry^^** units that are not in combat to be the targets.
Each target can move D6". Each target cannot move into combat during any part of that move.

Pick up to 3 friendly **^^Saurus^^** or **^^Kroxigor^^** units that are in combat to be the targets.

For each target:
• Make a pile-in move.
• Then, pick an enemy unit in combat with the target and roll a D3. On a 2+, inflict an amount of mortal damage on that enemy unit equal to the roll.
Ignore modifiers to save rolls for this unit (positive and negative).
If this unit charged this turn, if a friendly unit wholly within 12" of this unit uses the ‘All-out Attack’ command in the combat phase, no command points are spent.

Add 2" to the Move characteristic of friendly **^^Seraphon Cavalry^^** and **^^Seraphon Monster^^** units for the rest of the phase if they are wholly within 12" of this unit at the start of the move.

Your Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Seraphon Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a point on the battlefield within 18" of them to be the target point, then make a casting roll of 2D6.

Draw a straight line between the target point and the closest part on the caster’s base. Roll a D3 for each unit (friendly and enemy) that has models passed across by this line. On a 2+, inflict an amount of mortal damage on that unit equal to the roll.
**^^Asterism^^**
**Companion** weapons used by friendly **^^Seraphon^^** units have **Crit (2 Hits)**.
Once Per Battle, Start of the Third Battle Round

You can use this ability if you meet the condition below that corresponds to the **^^Asterism^^** you picked in the deployment phase.
***Itzl the Tamer:*** 3 or more enemy units have been destroyed.
***Quetzl the Preserver:*** There are no enemy units wholly within friendly territory.
***Sotek the Deliverer:*** The enemy general is in combat or has been destroyed.
***Tepok the Seer:*** There are any friendly **^^Slann^^** units on the battlefield and no friendly **^^Slann^^** units are in combat or have been destroyed.
Pick a different **^^Asterism^^** ability. It can be used in addition to the one you picked in the deployment phase.
Once Per Battle, Deployment Phase
Pick an **^^Asterism^^** ability.
That **^^Asterism^^** ability can be used for the rest of the battle, but the others cannot, unless allowed by the ‘Further the Great Plan’ ability.
